&lt;div&gt;The Data Integrator in this role will be at the core of support for AFSOC data initiatives. The Data Integrator will work closely with stakeholders and colleagues to gather requirements and identify solutions for a variety of data related projects. The work in this role has a direct impact on the AFSOC mission as it improves the command&#39;s ability to make data driven decisions.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Data Integrators are responsible for conducting methodology development, software requirement generation, tool testing, and the discovery, aggregation, and visualization of disparate data sources.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data Integrators will perform the following duties:&lt;/p&gt;
