&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with CI/CD pipelines and Git-based workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;TS/SCI clearance preferred; must be eligible to obtain TS/SCI with CI Poly within 6 months of hire&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;U.S. citizenship required&lt;/li&gt;
